article.headline: Marist 72, Cornell 67
article.story: POUGHKEEPSIE, N.Y. (AP) -- Will McClurkin and Will Whittington scored 15 points each to lead Marist over Cornell 72-67 on Friday night. The Red Foxes (1-0) shot 52 percent from the field and led by up to 20 points before Cornell went on a late run to close the gap to one. Lenny Collins scored 30 points for the Big Red (0-1).
